## Architecture

```
Phase 1: ScenarioClusterer (implemented)
├─ Load intervention history
├─ Normalize and tokenize queries
├─ Cluster similar patterns with Jaccard-style similarity
└─ Identify unmatched clusters

Phase 2: CLI Integration (implemented)
├─ rgen --suggest-scenarios
├─ JSON output
├─ text preview output
└─ file export

Phase 3: Tests + Docs (implemented)
├─ Unit tests
├─ Integration tests
└─ README examples
```

